    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review care offered to disabled people in hospital",
        "additional_details": "Although we value the work of the NHS, we believe people have to battle to get the care that disabled people deserve in hospital and a review needs to look into this.",
        "background": "We would like the Government to conduct a review of the care offered to disabled people in hospitals. This should look at how to ensure sufficient support, care and understanding is delivered to disabled people in hospital. ",
